Package: cobbled
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Cobble — Pebble smartwatch BLE daemon
 Connects to a Pebble smartwatch over Bluetooth Low Energy and runs as a
 user service providing time sync, desktop-notification forwarding, and an
 AppMessage bridge over D-Bus.
 .
 The daemon links libdbus statically; there is no runtime libdbus dependency.
 BlueZ is accessed through the system D-Bus.

Package: cobble
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, cobbled,
         libwayland-client0, libxkbcommon0
Description: Cobble — Pebble smartwatch GUI
 A Slint GUI front-end for the Cobble Pebble daemon. Displays synced health
 data (steps, sleep, workouts), watch info and battery level, and edits the
 daemon configuration. Talks to the cobbled daemon over the session D-Bus and
 reads the health database directly.
 .
 Uses the software renderer; launch it from a terminal with `cobble`.
